17
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,500
恋とか愛とかまとめて全部
Romance and love, everything altogether

18
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,500
君を置いてどこかに行っちゃうとか
Leaving you behind and going somewhere...

19
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,500
ありえないよ
that's impossible

20
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:13,200
君がくれた音に 弾けた火花に
To the sound you gave me, to the bursting sparks

21
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:16,800
はじめましてから ずっと恋しちゃってるんだよ
I've been in love with you ever since we first met

22
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:20,500
君のいない未来考えらんないよ
I can't imagine a future without you

23
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:24,000
これから先も二人がいいじゃん
Wouldn't it be great if it was the two of us from now on?

24
